{"lemma":"أَجارَة","slug":"أَجارَة","root":"#.ج.ر","root_slug":"_-ج-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ج-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n279","n281","n6668"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَجَرَ (ʔajara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of أَجَارَ (ʔajāra) (form IV)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"protection, patronage"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"alternative form of إِجَّار (ʔijjār, “roof”)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of أَجَرَ (ʔajara) or أَجَارَ (ʔajāra)."},"ipa":["/ʔi.d͡ʒaː.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n279","headword_ar":"اـِجَارَةٌ","root":"Ajr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaArapN","text_ar":"اَجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ujaArapN","text_ar":"اُجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajorN","text_ar":"اَجْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijaArapN","text_ar":"اـِجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"giving of usufructs for a compensation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land which its owners have let to him who will build upon it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so explained by the lawyers. (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n281","headword_ar":"اـِجَّارَةٌ","root":"Ajr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ij~aArN","text_ar":"اـِجَّارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n6668","headword_ar":"اجارهُ","root":"jwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ijaArapN","text_ar":"اـِجَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaArapN","text_ar":"جَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kr, K,) [or the latter is rather a quasi-inf. n., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAEapN","text_ar":"طَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTaAEahu","text_ar":"اَطَاعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He protected him; granted him refuge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preserved, saved, rescued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liberated, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K;) from ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":") wrongful, unjust, injurious, or tyrannical, treatment; (S, K;) from punishment; (S, A;) or from what he feared: (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he aided him; succoured him; delivered him from evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a","text_ar":"اَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"having a privative effect. (Mgh.) It is said of God,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yujiyru","text_ar":"يُجِيرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA yujaAru Ealayohi","text_ar":"وَلَا يُجَارُ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He protects, but none is protected against him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And in the Kur [lxxii. 22],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qulo A_in~iY lano yujiyraniY mina A@ll~`hi A^aHadN","text_ar":"قُلْ اـِنِّى لَنْ يُجِيرَنِى مِنَ ا@للّٰهِ اَحَدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily none will protect me against God."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjAr AlmataAEa","text_ar":"اجار المَتَاعَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the household-goods,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commodities, into the repository,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so preserved them from being lost."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  It is said [of God] in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yujiyru bayona AlbuHuwri","text_ar":"يُجِيرُ بَيْنَ البُحُورِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He makes a division between the seas, and prevents one from mixing with another and encroaching upon it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","K","Kr","Msb","TA"]}]}}